HOWTOINSTALL MAVENONUBUNTU-AWS

a. Create an ec2 instance
- First we create a key pair. key pairs allow us to ssh/login into the instance.
- The keypair is then download to your download folder on your computer
- Creating the ec2 instance

b. Connect to the instance and install apache maven
To connect your aws ec2 instances, you need the following parameters:
- The keypair: my keypair is prof.pem
- The server: ubuntu
- Ip or dns of the server
- Open an ssh client- most preferably- git bash
- Server url: ssh-i "prof.pem" ubuntu@ec2-99-79-7-165.ca-central-1.compute.amazonaws.com 

c. How to connect to the instance
- Open git bash
d. Change directory to Downloads
- cd  Downloads
e. Copy and paste the example link from aws cloud 
- ssh-i "prof.pem" ubuntu@ec2-99-79-7-165.ca-central-1.compute.amazonaws.com 

  Install apache maven
HOW TO INSTALL MAVEN ON UBUNTU - AWS

f. Update the system
- sudo apt update
g. Install java
- sudo apt install default-jdk
h. Verify Java Installation
- java  --version
i. Change directory to the opt directory
- cd  /opt
j. Download maven 3.9.12 from the apache maven website
- sudo wget https://dlcdn.apache.org/maven/maven-3/3.9.12/binaries/apache-maven-3.9.12-bin.tar.gz
k. Extract the Maven package
- sudo tar xf apache-maven-3.9.12-bin.tar.gz
l. Rename and create a soft link
- sudo ln -s /opt/apache-maven-3.9.12 /opt/maven
m. Remove the Apache Maven tar file
- sudo rm -rf apache-maven-3.9.12-bin.tar.gz
n. Perform Maven configuration
- sudo vi /etc/profile.d/maven.sh
o. Paste the following lines in maven.sh:

export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-21-openjdk-amd64 
export M2_HOME=/opt/maven
export MAVEN_HOME=/opt/maven
export PATH=${JAVA_HOME}/bin:${M2_HOME}/bin:${PATH}

p. Make the script executable
- sudo chmod +x /etc/profile.d/maven.sh
q. Load the environment variables
- source /etc/profile.d/maven.sh
r. Verify Maven installation
- mvn --version

If you this a result like this below congratulations you have successfully installed and setup maven.

Apache Maven 3.9.12 (848fbb4bf2d427b72bdb2471c22fced7ebd9a7a1)
Maven home: /opt/maven
